Pre-Game Insights: The match between Morocco and Sierra Leone looks to be an exciting battle between the determined spirit of Sierra Leone and Morocco’s well-honed tactics.
Morocco, renowned for their fairytale run in the FIFA World Cup aims to dominate the AFCON.
Sierra Leone seek to defy the odds in this friendly before the AFCON tournament.
Kick-off is scheduled for Thursday, 11th January 2024, at 5:00 PM GMT; 10:30 PM IST at Stade de San Pédro.
Miscellaneous Highlights: In their last 5 games, Morocco have beaten Sierra Leone thrice. Sierra Leone have only won the match once.
Sierra Leone have conceded 14 goals in their last 5 games and scored 3 goals only.
Morocco have conceded 4 goals in their last 5 games.
Others: Achraf Hakimi is an adaptable full-back who excels at counter attacks and displays unwavering pace and accuracy.
Rodney Michael embodies pace and tenacity, contributing significantly up front.
The match prediction favors Morocco with a 2-1 win.
